{"tid":1043571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾翡翠家居 即刻寄電郵消委會投訴佢","createTime":"2019-03-02T11:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T12:12:06.000Z","uid":170886,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1592174a221fb730ee93584365632a15f004df","tid":1043571,"uid":170886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母垃圾翡翠家居<br />\n成6000蚊買個櫃, 你都可以櫃桶整到唔撚同色<br />\n唔同色都算啦,我當你過年前趕貨,做野趕跟唔到咁多<br />\n打電話上去,起碼叫做好聲好氣咁話叫師傅上黎換左佢<br />\n3月頭打電話,今日先黎收,都算撚數啦<br />\n<br />\n今日返到屋企,工人姐姐話個師傅直接拆左面板走<br />\n話要度尺寸,留返兩個大窿比我<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/191600_580fd6bbe6d8a12d2a1fe54d3190c825.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F191600_580fd6bbe6d8a12d2a1fe54d3190c825.JPG&h=6adb1b42&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我未見過咁ON9既師傅,你度尺寸唔可以直接攞尺出來度?要成塊板拆左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話要半個月先俾番我,等我鋪足半個月既塵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經即刻寄電郵消委會投訴佢,有無其他人一樣中過伏?<br />\n一世唔會再買佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438100a56e3d54468b6bad9787c884b0f5bbea02","tid":1043571,"uid":24632,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"先唔講間野，平定貴<br />\n點解個櫃個款咁肉酸樓主都買得落手？"},{"pid":"06a9d14fbec814f5f981f6a9a10dc7ec2a9436f2","tid":1043571,"uid":170886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"438100a56e3d54468b6bad9787c884b0f5bbea02","tid":1043571,"uid":24632,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"先唔講間野，平定貴<br />\n點解個櫃個款咁肉酸樓主都買得落手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:25:04.000Z","msg":"頂,實木櫃,無咩款揀<br />\n屋企人俾錢,唔係我話事"},{"pid":"ecc685146c0515ac1d063ea9d5b00d8f9f4a8699","tid":1043571,"uid":190540,"l